LavaClient 1.3.0 API

Packages 
Package Description
samophis.lavalink.client.entities
Contains all the entities and their implementations LavaClient uses.
samophis.lavalink.client.entities.builders
Contains all the builders LavaClient uses both internally and exposes publicly to construct entities.
samophis.lavalink.client.entities.events
Contains all the event classes and the listener/adapter classes for them.
samophis.lavalink.client.entities.internal
Contains internal implementations for entities not meant to be used (or even seen) by the end user.
samophis.lavalink.client.entities.messages.client
Contains all the messages LavaClient sends to AudioNodes.
samophis.lavalink.client.entities.messages.server
Contains all the messages Lavalink-Server sends to LavaClient (except events).
samophis.lavalink.client.exceptions
Contains all the Exception classes LavaClient makes use of.
samophis.lavalink.client.util
Contains utility singletons/classes which contain helpful code independent of other classes.
